<h2>Who We Are</h2>
<p>
    We are a family owned local pizza restaurant which has proudly served the citizens of Montréal through our one location in Sainte-Anne-de-Bellevue for 60 years, and still counting.
    Over the course of our time as a business, we have put smiles on the faces of countless people by doing what we do best: producing the greatest pies that one can acquire in the province of Québec!
</p>
