<h2>Our History</h2>
<p>
    The one and only location which we use to satisfy customers was founded during August 23, 1961. Whereas most pizza restaurants aim to expand by developing chains,
    we have always sought growth through improving our methods of food preparation and experimenting with new recipes to produce the highest quality products possible,
    and introduce our customers to all-new flavours.
</p>
